{"tid":2054642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿日本拒批評中國硬推國安法 ，本田圭佑為港發聲","createTime":"2020-06-07T10:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T10:59:47.000Z","uid":30040,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5c1c595a64a1184e9b2c01452c8a1b44d385ab","tid":2054642,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:16:57.000Z","msg":"北京硬推「港版國安法」受到西方社會關注，但有報道指日本政府卻拒絕參與，由美英提出的聯合聲明批評中國。日本球星本田圭佑周日就在社交媒體為港發聲，表示不滿日本無原因地拒絕簽署聲明。<br />\n日本共同社報道，指日本政府曾被詢問，會否參與由美英提出，批評中國硬推「港版國安法」的聲明，但日方表示拒絕，有指因日本希望與中國改善關係，所以沒有跟隨英美國家。<br />\n目前效力巴甲保地花高的日本球星本田圭佑，周日就在Twitter分享了這篇，日本政府拒絕參加批評中國硬推「港版國安法」聲明的報道，更寫上：「為甚麼日本拒絕參與批評中國的聲明！聽到值得犧牲香港民主都要拒絕的理由前，我是不能接受的。」他分享新聞時亦擔心消息是否屬實，他更指：「假如這篇報道屬實，日本就有嚴重的問題；但如果報道不實，共同社就有嚴重的問題。」"},{"pid":"744bf0527d08af6dd4a8f9d8ddc8239331a5506f","tid":2054642,"uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200607/XRX2TR5ZT32GUZV7KFGFBLAFVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200607%2FXRX2TR5ZT32GUZV7KFGFBLAFVY%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=ce4f6cd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200607%2FXRX2TR5ZT32GUZV7KFGFBLAFVY%2F&h=a1ac47af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200607/XRX2TR5ZT32GUZV7KFGFBLAFVY/</a>"},{"pid":"806b6e12f0d1dcd40afdb9a48661e8cd7f15410e","tid":2054642,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kskgroup2017/status/1269434728467349505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkskgroup2017%2Fstatus%2F1269434728467349505&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f88c22ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkskgroup2017%2Fstatus%2F1269434728467349505&h=eaddf8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kskgroup2017/status/1269434728467349505</a>"},{"pid":"8ce351141c952cd1a934bf879ea373fd180d5906","tid":2054642,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"慘"}]}